Generally speaking , you may modify browser preferences to accept all cookies , be notified when a cookie is set , or to reject all cookies .
If you choose to reject all cookies , you may be unable to use many of AccuWeather 's products and services .
Some sections of the AccuWeather Sites may require that you log on in order to continue to use specific goods or services offered through our network , because we do not want cookies to replace security measures that you would otherwise take for yourself , your PII and your data .
