back to top of page Definitions Aggregate Information .
Aggregate information means information about groups or categories of guests , which does not identify and can not reasonably be used to identify an individual guest .
back to top of page Anonymous Information .
Anonymous information means information that does not directly or indirectly identify , and can not reasonably be used to identify , an individual guest .
back to top of page Application .
Application means a program or service operated by us ( or on our behalf ) that may be displayed on various online , mobile or other platforms and environments , including those operated by third parties , which permits us to interact directly with our guests .
back to top of page Children .
Children means individuals who we have identified are not of legal age to consent to the collection and processing of their personal information .
In the United States and Latin America , the term children refers to individuals under 13 years of age .
